1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object recognition and pose estimation using convolutional neural networks. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the application of the proposed method in cluttered environments, which is relevant to robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new loss function for descriptor learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with object recognition and pose estimation, which are important tasks in AI. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the use of surface normals as an image modality.
